# Lugaru, with Flydigi Apex 2 in  mind
mousecalibration 130
ingamemouse 1

CamXY mouse 100
ActionWheelXY flick # Flick with wheel
mousepriority flick # Disable normal camera motion while using wheel
flickdeadzone 40

JoyXY WASD deadzone 40 # Move

BumperL Shift # Crouch
BumperR Q # Throw
TriggerL Space # Jump
TriggerR M1 # Attack

ActionH E # Draw

MenuR Escape # Pause
